msgid "Management interface reference"
msgstr "管理界面参考"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/management-interface-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Various Quarkus extensions contribute non-application endpoints that provide different kinds of information about the application.\n"
"Examples of such extensions are the xref:smallrye-health.adoc[health], xref:telemetry-micrometer.adoc[metrics], xref:openapi-swaggerui.adoc[OpenAPI] and xref:info.adoc[info] extensions."
msgstr "各种 Quarkus 扩展提供了非应用程序端点，这些端点可提供有关应用程序的各类信息。此类扩展的示例包括 xref:smallrye-health.adoc[健康状态] 、 xref:telemetry-micrometer.adoc[指标] 、 xref:openapi-swaggerui.adoc[OpenAPI] xref:info.adoc[和信息] 扩展。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/management-interface-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "These non-application endpoints are normally accessible under the `/q` prefix like so:"
msgstr "这些非应用程序端点通常可通过 `/q` 前缀访问，如下所示："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/management-interface-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`/q/health`"
msgstr "`/q/健康`"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/management-interface-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`/q/metrics`"
msgstr "`/q/metrics`"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/management-interface-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`/q/openapi`"
msgstr "`/q/openapi`"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/management-interface-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`/q/info`"
msgstr "`/q/info`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/management-interface-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"By default, these management endpoints are served by the same HTTP server as your application endpoints.\n"
"This document presents how you can use a separate HTTP server (bound to a different network interface and port) for the management endpoints.\n"
"It avoids exposing these endpoints on the main server and, therefore, prevents undesired accesses."
msgstr "默认情况下，这些管理端点由与应用程序端点相同的 HTTP 服务器提供服务。本文介绍了如何为管理端点使用独立的 HTTP 服务器（绑定到不同的网络接口和端口）。这样可以避免在主服务器上暴露这些端点，从而防止不受欢迎的访问。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/management-interface-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Enabling the management interface"
msgstr "启用管理界面"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/management-interface-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To enable the management interface, use the following **build-time** property:"
msgstr "要启用管理界面，请使用以下 *构建时* 属性："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/management-interface-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"By default, management endpoints will be exposed on: `http://0.0.0.0:9000/q`.\n"
"For example, if you have `smallrye-health` installed, the readiness probe will be exposed at `http://0.0.0.0:9000/q/health/ready`."
msgstr "默认情况下，管理端点将通过以下地址对外暴露： `http://0.0.0.0:9000/q` 。例如，如果您安装了 `smallrye-health` ，则就绪性探针将通过 `http://0.0.0.0:9000/q/health/ready` 对外暴露。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/management-interface-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "SmallRye Health Checks, Micrometer and Info endpoints will be declared as management endpoints when the management interface is enabled."
msgstr "启用管理接口后，SmallRye Health Checks、Micrometer 和 Info 端点将被声明为管理端点。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/management-interface-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The management interface is disabled when no extensions relying on it (such as the SmallRye Health or SmallRye OpenAPI extensions) are installed."
msgstr "如果未安装任何依赖该管理界面的扩展（例如 SmallRye Health 或 SmallRye OpenAPI 扩展），则该管理界面将被禁用。"

